.1em;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><span leaf=\"\">字数 754，阅读大约需 4 分钟</span></p>\n   </blockquote>\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: hsl(var(--border));margin: 1.5em 8px;user-select: text !important;text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Menlo, Monaco, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><span leaf=\"\">现在播客节目都很夸张，动辄2-3个小时。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: hsl(var(--border));margin: 1.5em 8px;user-select: text !important;text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Menlo, Monaco, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><span leaf=\"\">大家时间宝贵，出现了很多 AI 播客总结工具。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: hsl(var(--border));margin: 1.5em 8px;user-select: text !important;text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Menlo, Monaco, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><span leaf=\"\">推荐一些个人用过的工具和使用方法。</span></p>\n   <h2 style=\"padding:0px 0.2em;margin:4em auto 2em;font-weight:bold;display:table;font-size:19.2px;border-color:hsl(var(--border));line-height:1.75;box-sizing:border-box;background:rgb(51, 51, 51);border-width:0px;font-family:Menlo, Monaco, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace;border-style:solid;user-select:text !important;text-align:center;\"><span leaf=\"\">Podquest</span></h2>\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: hsl(var(--border));margin: 1.5em 8px;user-select: text !important;text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Menlo, Monaco, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><span leaf=\"\">免费拿到大量海内外播客的音频转写文本，简直活菩萨。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;bor