er New&quot;, monospace;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><span leaf=\"\">阅读群一个群友开发的工具。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: hsl(var(--border));margin: 1.5em 8px;user-select: text !important;text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Menlo, Monaco, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><span leaf=\"\">虽然收录播客不够全，但比较有趣的是，会用AI提炼播客内容，生成金句卡片。</span></p>\n   <figure style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: hsl(var(--border));margin: 1.5em 8px;user-select: text !important;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Menlo, Monaco, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace;font-size: 16px;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\">\n    <span leaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"501959066\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/ff138297-592d-41e8-2b15-dc743f0dbb00/public\" data-type=\"png\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: hsl(var(--border));display: block;vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;height: auto;user-select: text !important;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Menlo, Monaco, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace;font-size: 16px;margin: 0.1em auto 0.5em;border-radius: 4px;\" title=\"null\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/ff138297-592d-41e8-2b15-dc743f0dbb00/public\"></span>\n    <figcaption style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: hsl(var(--border));user-select: text !important;text-align: center;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Menlo, Monaco, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace;font-size: 0.8em;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"></figcaption>\n   </figure>\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: hsl(var(--border));margin: 1.5em 8px;user-select: text !important;text-align: jus