tyle:solid;user-select:text !important;text-align:center;\"><span leaf=\"\">如何生成双语对照字幕？</span></h2>\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: hsl(var(--border));margin: 1.5em 8px;user-select: text !important;text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Menlo, Monaco, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><span leaf=\"\">有些播客内容觉得实在是好，AI总结会丢掉大量细节。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: hsl(var(--border));margin: 1.5em 8px;user-select: text !important;text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Menlo, Monaco, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><span leaf=\"\">这时建议把字幕做成双语对照版，放到飞书文档慢慢读。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: hsl(var(--border));margin: 1.5em 8px;user-select: text !important;text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Menlo, Monaco, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><span leaf=\"\">比如上面分享的纳瓦尔最新访谈，3小时长的播客文本，只有 Gemini 可以快速搞定。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: hsl(var(--border));margin: 1.5em 8px;user-select: text !important;text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Menlo, Monaco, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><span leaf=\"\">100w token上下文窗口还是很爽。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: hsl(var(--border));margin: 1.5em 8px;user-select: text !important;text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Menlo, Monaco, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><span leaf=\"\">即使这样，也让AI继续了三次，花了接近15分钟才翻译完成。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: hsl(var(--border));margin: 1.5em 8px;user-select: text !important;text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Menlo, Monaco, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><span leaf=\"\">提示词：</span></p>\n   <pre style=\"padding:0px !important;margin:10px 8px;font-size:14px;border-color:hsl(var(--border));line-height:1.5;box-sizing:border-box;font-variation-settings:normal;border-radius:8px;font-feature-settings:normal;overflow-x:auto;border-width:0px;font-family:Menlo, Monaco, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace;border-style:solid;user-select:text !important;text-align:left;\"><code style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: hsl(var(--border));font-family: Menlo, &quot;Operator Mono&quot;, Consolas, Monaco, monospace;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-size: 16px;user-select: text !important;display: -webkit-box;padding: 0.5em 1em 1em;overflow-x: auto;text-indent: 0px;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;margin: 0px;white-space: nowrap;\"><span leaf=\"\">你是一位专业的中英双语翻译专家，精通中英文语言和文化。将以下英文转换为中英对照格式，要求：</span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: hsl(var(--border));user-select: text !important;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: hsl(var(--border));user-select: text !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">1. 将每个语义单元分为英文原文和中文翻译两行呈现，这是对话文本，需要区分说话人。</span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: hsl(var(--border));user-select: text !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">2. 对CET6或以上水平的词汇，直接在英语单词后用括号标注中文简短释义</span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: hsl(var(--border));user-select: text !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">3. 对俚语、文化典故或特殊表达，在中文翻译的下一行加入简短解释</span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: hsl(var(--border));user-select: text !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">4. 内容Chris Williamson访谈Naval Ravikant的文本（Youtube自动生成的英文，可能存在错误，需要你纠正）</span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: hsl(var(--border));user-select: text !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">5. 保持翻译的准确性和自然流畅度，同时忠实原文</span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: hsl(var(--border));user-select: text !important;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: hsl(var(--border));user-select: text !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">以下是需要翻译的内容：{{content}}</span></code></pre>\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: hsl(var(--border));margin: 1.5em 8px;user-select: text !important;text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Menlo, Monaco, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: hsl(var(--border));font-weight: bold;user-select: text !important;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Menlo, Monaco, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"><span leaf=\"\">最新纳瓦尔3小时访谈双语对照：</span></strong></p>\n   <blockquote style=\"padding:1em;margin:0px 0px 1em;border-left-color:rgb(51, 51, 51);font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;border-radius:6px;border-width:0px 0px 0px 4px;font-family:Menlo, Monaco, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace;border-style:solid;user-select:text !important;text-align:left;\">\n    <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: hsl(var(--border));margin: 0px;user-select: text !important;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Menlo, Monaco, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace;font-size: 1em;display: block;letter